49
00:02:30,520 --> 00:02:35,520
Lord, thou hast been our dwelling place in all generations.

50
00:02:36,399 --> 00:02:39,119
And so even as you read verse number one,

51
00:02:39,119 --> 00:02:42,639
though El Olam, the everlasting God is not mentioned

52
