61
00:03:05,160 --> 00:03:07,880
that these truths of creation,

62
00:03:07,880 --> 00:03:09,360
he'll say in the very next phrase,

63
00:03:09,360 --> 00:03:13,919
or ever thou hast formed the earth and the world,

64
00:03:13,919 --> 00:03:15,880
God is the creator.

65
00:03:15,880 --> 00:03:18,880
And the psalmist is acknowledging

66
00:03:18,880 --> 00:03:22,800
that before this took place, before the creation,

67
00:03:22,800 --> 00:03:25,759
