167
00:08:19,799 --> 00:08:21,880
Isn't that a great verse of scripture?

168
00:08:21,880 --> 00:08:26,760
I mean, our God is so great, he's so wonderful.

169
00:08:26,760 --> 00:08:30,440
He is the everlasting God, he is the creator.

170
00:08:30,440 --> 00:08:34,919
He does not faint, he does not grow weary, hallelujah.

171
00:08:34,919 --> 00:08:37,599
And the Bible tells us there's no searching

172
00:08:37,599 --> 00:08:38,479
