00:10:01,440 --> 00:10:04,440
And so I want you to rejoice and to rest in this covenant.

202
00:10:04,440 --> 00:10:06,239
And I'll give it this way to you.

203
00:10:06,239 --> 00:10:09,239
Number two, because he is the everlasting God,

